This is the first iteration of the java API for the Viadeo REST API.

For now, it's a read-only API, we didn't need more. Feel free to improve it.

To use it with maven, just add the repository :

<repositories>
  <repository>
    <id>StandInnovation</id>
    <name>Stand Innovation maven repository</name>
    <url>http://maven.stand-innovation.org/maven/ </url>
</repositories>

<dependencies>
  ...
  <dependency>
    <groupId>com.clevercloud</groupId>
    <artifactId>viadeo4j</artifactId>
    <version>1.1</version>
  </dependency>
  ...
<dependencies>
